##########################
#### This is the Code ####
##########################
Django application name: simple_qa

Files:
URL configuration:  'simple_qa/urls.py'
Models:             'simple_qa/models.py'
Views:              'simple_qa/views.py'
Forms:              'simple_qa/forms.py'
Templates:          'templates/simple_qa/*'
CSS:                'site_media/css/*'
Graphics:           'site_media/gfx/*'


